description:
To read “The Inner Clock” and other SciShow recommended reading, go to https://bookshop.org/lists/scishow-recommended-reading.

Have you ever wondered where giant beasties of folklore, like the chupacabra, came from? Not every mythological creature has a scientific explanation, but here are a few that might.

Hosted by: Reid Reimers (he/him)
